<tool id="ometiff_validation" name="Validate" version="0.0.1">
  <description> an OME.TIFF</description>
  <command interpreter="bash">
    ometiff_validator.sh $dataset
  </command>
  <inputs>
    <param name="dataset" type="data" label="Choose an image for validation" multiple="false" optional="false" />
  </inputs>
  <outputs>
    <data format="tiff" name="output" from_work_dir="image.ome.tif"/>
  </outputs>
<tests>
  <test>
    <param name="dataset" value="image.ome.tif" ftype="tiff"/>
    <output name="image">
         <assert_contents>
             <not_has_text text="Error" />
         </assert_contents>
    </output>
  </test>
</tests>

<help>
**Description**

Validate the file using xmlvalid from BioFormats.

-----

**Input**

An OME.TIFF file.

-----

**Output**

If true, then a valid OME.TIFF file.
</help>
</tool>
